      "commit": {
        "parents": [
          {
            "commit": "eb39d82ae13ddb6010065cede13dca11f1da6aaf",
            "subject": "LU-2272 statahead: ll_intent_drop_lock() called in spinlock"
          }
        ],
        "author": {
          "name": "Alexander.Boyko",
          "email": "alexander_boyko@xyratex.com",
          "date": "2014-05-28 17:52:13.000000000",
          "tz": 240
        },
        "committer": {
          "name": "Oleg Drokin",
          "email": "oleg.drokin@intel.com",
          "date": "2014-06-11 19:42:59.000000000",
          "tz": 0
        },
        "subject": "LU-5116 ptlrpc: race at req processing",
        "message": "LU-5116 ptlrpc: race at req processing\n\nRace between ptlrpc_resend_req() and ptlrpc_check_set().\n1 thread do ptlrpc_check_set()->after_reply()\n2 thread do ptlrpc_resend_req()\nThe result is request with rq_resend = 1 and MSG_REPLY flag.\nWhen this request will came to server it will cause client eviction.\nThe patch skip ptlrpc_resend_req logic if rq_replied is set,\nand clear rq_resend flag at reply_in_callback() when client got\nreply.\n\nSigned-off-by: Alexander Boyko <alexander_boyko@xyratex.com>\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-1888\nChange-Id: If47b9a1f559ab16e4b416332ada7c73a8758d46c\nReviewed-on: http://review.whamcloud.com/10471\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <andreas.dilger@intel.com>\nTested-by: Jenkins\nTested-by: Maloo <hpdd-maloo@intel.com>\nReviewed-by: Mike Pershin <mike.pershin@intel.com>\nReviewed-by: Chris Horn <hornc@cray.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <oleg.drokin@intel.com>\nReviewed-on: http://review.whamcloud.com/10562\nReviewed-by: James Nunez <james.a.nunez@intel.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_5"
    }
  },
